            <p class="text-muted">Dallas, Texas - The coding-for-charity idea is hatched by Chris Koenig, Developer Evangelist for Microsoft, as a way to channel the raw energy of the software developers to benefit the local community. The concept would eventually be known as GiveCamp.</p>
