            <h4 class="subheading">Taking Shape</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-body">
            <p class="text-muted">Dallas, Texas - Dallas ASP.NET User Group leader Toi Wright organized and ran the first ever event, named &quot;We Are Microsoft Charity Challenge Weekend.&quot; The event served 18 charities with over 80 volunteers!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
