            <h4 class="subheading">The Idea Spreads</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-body">
            <p class="text-muted">Kansas City, Kansas - The second coding-for-charity event, &quot;Coders 4 Charities,&quot; is held in Kansas City. Twenty-five volunteers implemented projects for five non-profits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
