            <h4 class="subheading">The Idea gets a Name</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-body">
            <p class="text-muted">Ann Arbor, Michigan - The first GiveCamp-titled event, Ann Arbor GiveCamp, is held at Washtenaw Community College in Ann Arbor, Michigan. The event, organized by Microsoft Developer Evangelist Jennifer Marsman, had served 15 charities through the help of over 90 volunteers, including remote locations in Columbus, Ohio and Knoxville, Tennessee.</p>
